Steps to create a tomcat role & 
================================
1) Create a directory for tomcat installation . eg: /opt/tomcat/
2) We have to download the apache tomcat from external source under a local path eg: /tmp/
3) We have to extract the file  under the path /opt/tomcat/
4) We need to upload the artifacts from the jenkins path (or) nexus artifact server to the tomcat standard location $TOMCAT_HOME/webapps/
5) Upload config files (if any) for the application
6) Finally start the tomcat service.



http://apache.mirror.digitalpacific.com.au/tomcat/tomcat-8/v8.5.46/bin/apache-tomcat-8.5.46.tar.gz

variables
===========
tomcat_download_base_path: "http://apache.mirror.digitalpacific.com.au/tomcat/tomcat-"
tomcat_version: "t"


